videos.description: Mitchell Wilbekin finds Doral Moore on the alley-oop feed for the Demon Deacons.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wilbekin, Moore connect for alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Doral Moore wakes up the crowd with a thunderous two-handed jam in transition.
videos.headline: Moore strikes again with a fast-break jam

videos.description: Oshae Brissett works through the Wake Forest zone and scores a right-handed layup for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Brissett slithers through D for layup

videos.description: Tyus Battle steals the pass, races the floor and lays down the hammer for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Battle with the steal and stuff

videos.description: Matthew Moyer makes a reverse right-handed layup for the Orange to cap an 11-3 run.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Moyer scores beautiful reverse layup

videos.description: Mitchell Wilbekin hits a 3-pointer and is fouled for a 4-point play opportunity.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wilbekin gets chance for 4-point play

videos.description: Oshae Brissett blocks the shot of Bryant Crawford in transition for the Orange.
videos.headline: Brissett denies Wake Forest's Crawford at the rim

videos.description: Matthew Moyer cuts to the rim, receives the pass from Frank Howard and dunks it for the Orange.
videos.headline: Moyer rocks the rim with a two-handed slam

videos.description: Mitchell Wilbekin drives to the lane and dishes to Bryant Crawford who buries a 3-pointer for the Demon Deacons.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wilbekin, Crawford combine for 3-pointer

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu receives the pass from Frank Howard and lays the hammer down for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Chukwu throws down nasty dunk in the paint

videos.description: Wake Forest head coach Danny Manning says the team's depth was the key in its first ever victory over Syracuse 73-67.
videos.headline: Manning on overcoming injuries: 'Next man up!'
